This is the very first working example. 
The pedestrian remembers all the visited places
and does nothing after exploring all.

The room map is in the file geometry.dat

To run this example do:

1) gcc -Wall -O3 -o hope_test.e hope_test.c -lm
   ./hope_test.e geometry.dat 1000
   
2)  gcc -Wall -O3 -o rule_target.e rule_target.c -lm
   ./rule_target.e geometry_map.lammpstrj
   
3) gcc -Wall -O3 -o move_test.e move_test.c -lm
   ./move_test.e geometry.dat geometry_rule.lammpstrj
   
4) chmod 775 run_movie
   ./run_movie geometry
   
You will get the movie of a single pedestrian in geometry.mp4.
Make sure you already installed ffmpeg and mogrify.
